WEBVTT

00:09:00.784 --> 00:09:04.118
All of the nation's big Wall Street firms
bet on these loans.

00:09:04.142 --> 00:09:05.316
At its peak,

00:09:05.340 --> 00:09:09.046
one out of every five mortgages
in the country was in this mold,

00:09:09.070 --> 00:09:11.149
and the crisis,

00:09:11.173 --> 00:09:14.691
the crisis that my colleagues
and I saw coming ...

00:09:16.133 --> 00:09:17.933
would go on to cost us all.

00:09:19.077 --> 00:09:23.077
Nineteen trillion in lost wealth.

00:09:24.633 --> 00:09:27.640
Pensions, home equity, savings.

00:09:28.426 --> 00:09:31.885
Eight million jobs vanished.